HEADWORD: Intoxicant
<hw>In*tox"i*cant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which
intoxicates; an intoxicating agent; <as>as, alcohol, opium, and laughing
gas are <ex>intoxicants</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

